@startuml
!include style.puml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "TutBook Application" {
  [UI] as UI
  [Logic] as Logic
  [Model] as Model
  [Storage] as Storage
  [Commons] as Commons
}

UI --> Logic : execute(command)
Logic --> Model : modify/query data
Model --> Storage : read/write JSON
Storage --> Model : load/save entities
Model --> UI : notify changes (ObservableList)

Commons ..> UI
Commons ..> Logic
Commons ..> Model
Commons ..> Storage
@enduml
